# Difference Between SNS and SES

| SNS | SES |
|-----|-----|
| Notification service | Email service |
| Supports SMS and notifications | Supports email sending |
| Uses Topics and Subscribers | Uses Email Identities |
| Message broadcasting | Email communication |
| Alerts and event messaging | Transactional and marketing emails |

